sql_text: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS agent_sandbox.tokyo_hourly_temp (time DATETIME, temperature_2m DOUBLE)

WITH diffs AS (SELECT LAG(`time`) OVER (ORDER BY `time`) AS from_time, `time` AS to_time, temperature_2m - LAG(temperature_2m) OVER (ORDER BY `time`) AS delta_c FROM agent_sandbox.tokyo_hourly_temp), endpoints AS (SELECT MIN(`time`) AS start_time, MAX(`time`) AS end_time FROM agent_sandbox.tokyo_hourly_temp), temps AS (SELECT e.start_time, s.temperature_2m AS start_temp, e.end_time, t.temperature_2m AS end_temp FROM endpoints e JOIN agent_sandbox.tokyo_hourly_temp s ON s.`time` = e.start_time JOIN agent_sandbox.tokyo_hourly_temp t ON t.`time` = e.end_time), biggest_drop AS (SELECT from_time, to_time, delta_c FROM diffs WHERE from_time IS NOT NULL ORDER BY delta_c ASC LIMIT 1) SELECT start_time, start_temp, end_time, end_temp, ROUND(end_temp - start_temp, 1) AS net_change_c, from_time AS biggest_drop_from, to_time AS biggest_drop_to, ROUND(delta_c, 1) AS biggest_drop_c FROM temps CROSS JOIN biggest_drop
